{
  "stem": "16930.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was a group home for boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they had other hostels and group homes for girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this being an Orthodox hostel, we had-- we went to a regular public school in daytime, but we also had several other shearim classes in Jewish subjects.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- we had prayers every day-- minyan to daven every day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we also had different shearim-- one in the morning before going to public school, and maybe a couple of shearim after coming back from public school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were quite busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we also had a-- got a good Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think around 25-- maybe 25 to 30.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Around 25, I would say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was located in Tylers Green, a small village near the town of High Wycombe, which was a known furniture town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they produced a lot of furniture there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what the town was known for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and in the village, we lived in a house called the Old Vicarage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This used-- next to a graveyard, next to a church, because the vicar used to live in that house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a big house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It had many rooms in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And therefore, it could hold 25, 30 kids, you know, even though there was several of-- of us in each room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like a dormitory style, five or six in a room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But even so, they could hold the-- the kids and the staff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And downstairs, there was living rooms, and the dining rooms, and also the areas where we had classes, [? in those room. ?]",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was run from a-- a private committee, from the Golders Green Beth Hamedrash, a synagogue in Golders Green, where the rabbi was Rabbi Leo Munk and the secretary was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
